data.description: Discover the potential of this charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home with a 2-car detached garage and a spacious backyard! Built for those who appreciate both character and opportunity, this property boasts a new roof with Art-Loc shingles from Sheriff Goslin Roofing in 2020, ensuring long-lasting protection. Inside, you'll find a cozy wood-burning stove in both the house and garage, perfect for those cozy evenings. Step outside onto the large covered porch, where you can enjoy the serene surroundings. This home has been upgraded from boiler heat to a modern furnace for your comfort. Additional features include a new vinyl fence, attic fan, and a new water heater. While it does need some work, this property offers endless possibilities and the chance to create your dream home. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!
